[I] Fwbuilder library

[T] libfwbuilder is the central library for Firewall Builder, a multi-platform
[T] firewall configuration and management tool.
[T] It provides a set of policy compilers for various firewall platforms,
[T] and currently supports iptables, ipfilter, OpenBSD PF and Cisco PIX.

[U] http://www.fwbuilder.org

[A] Vadim Kurland <vadim@fwbuilder.org>
[M] The T2 Project <t2@t2-project.org>

